  "detail": {
    "tagExpireTime": "1755063237860",
    "endLabelIds": "",
    "endLabelNames": "",
    "title": "冷柜、商用电器品类POP店铺升降级机制公告",
    "followRuleId": "1265575883712892928",
    "content": "<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-indent: 20pt; line-height: 200%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">为鼓励商家提升价格竞争力及销售额，对冷柜、商用电器品类POP店铺建立店铺升降级机制，核心考核销售额指标，价格竞争力和广告投放金额作为观测指标，表现优秀的专卖店可升级为旗舰店，表现不好的旗舰店降级为专卖店。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">一、 适用商家范围</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-indent: 20pt; line-height: 200%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">在京东开放平台完成开店并启用时间超过6个月，主营类目冷柜或商用电器的POP旗舰店、专卖店。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">二、 适用类目</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-indent: 20pt; line-height: 200%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">家用电器-大家电-冷柜（类目id：12392）、家用电器-商用电器（类目id：14857）、商用电器（类目id：44737）。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">三、 考核周期</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2025</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">年9月起，月度考核一次，结束时间另行通知。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">四、 考核规则</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">旗舰店降级规则</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">冷柜、商用电器主营类目下的店铺，单月GMV低于50万且连续3个月负同比的店铺降级为专卖店。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">专卖店升级规则</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">① 连续三个月GMV大于50万且连续三个月同比均为正则可以申请升级为旗舰店；</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">② 店铺可获取到品牌方出具的旗舰店开店授权。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">五、 相关说明</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">商家采取不正当手段（如刷单、套券、乱挂等）获得的店铺升级机会，不予升级。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">商家存在恶意竞争、影响消费者权益、影响京东声誉等违反市场公平竞争原则、诚实信用原则、公序良俗的行为，及存在价格虚高、严重质量问题等不予升级。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">3.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">考核周期内所有销售额计算口径都会剔除疑似刷单、套利的销售额。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">4.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">考核周期内获得升级机会的专卖店，需要取得品牌方旗舰店授权，才可以最终升级为旗舰店。</span></p>",
